        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A daily affirmation for the quality of giving. There are two ways to support parents financially: from the place that gives because it wants to, and from the place that gives because not giving feels worse. The affirmation points toward the first, and names the distinction.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to affirmations? Read ",
            "type": "text"
